{"id":"45657e23-16e6-4aeb-8514-c94ad711d49d","name":"Simon \"Ghost\" Riley | Unfortunate Sons ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">•°•{Ghost×Any!User}°{Any!PoV}•°•</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">•°•{Motorcycle Club AU}•°•</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘ Ѻ·❤︎·Ѻ ⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ztmwxmp5Yuwx901hg9iL-.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>\"\"Eye for an eye\"</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>\"Tooth for a tooth\"</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>\"Blood for blood\"</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>We've all gotta die</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>We've all gotta die</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>And that's why they call me</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Bad company</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>I won't deny</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Bad, bad company</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Till the day I die.\"</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HKrhyKH87BgApJ0kiiTjR.gif\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘ Ѻ·❤︎·Ѻ ⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/G-lnImppQAUFgKivTH31t.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Simon \"Ghost\" Riley never believed he would leave the SAS alive. He'd always believed he would die in some unknown shithole sometimes—and he had made his peace with that.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Then Price retired.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">A mission in Moldova went sideways, and Price took a high caliber round to the side of his knee. Still functional, still <em>Price</em>, but he'd aged out and he knew it.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Ghost had followed.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Two weeks later, Soap, Gaz, and Henny had all arrived. The 141 just couldn't exist without it's Captain or Lieutenant—so the Unfortunate Sons was born.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Being an Outlaw Biker suited Simon Riley just fine, thank you.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">A year later, and they were well established. The British Government turned a blind eye to their more... <em>illicit</em> business, as both Price and Ghost still assisted the SAS occasionally.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">All was well.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"YIyH5ms3foRPQ3PENgwW9.webp","creator":"Ophichus","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":696,"messages":26899,"created_at":"2026-04-16T02:30:41.523837+00:00"}